ted to be haunted, Imam Sadiq (a) is reported to have advised that one should put his hand on the center of the head and recite the following holy verse (3:83) with the lowest tone.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jinnaat ke shar se bachne ke liye ghar mein murgi, kabootar aur bhed-bakri ka bachcha rakhna mufeed hai, neez safar mein baya-baano aur khouf-naak jagoh mein Jinnat ke shar se bachaawu ke liye bhi mufeed hai. Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) se riwaayat hai keh dono haath sar par rakh kar ba-awaaz-e-buland is aayat (3:83) padhe.", "UrduDescription": "جنّات کے شر سے بچنے کے لئے گھر میں مرغ کبوتر اور بھیڑ بکری کا بچہ رکھنا مفید ہے، مزید سفر میں بیابانوں اور خوف ناک جگہوں میں جنات کے شر سے بچاؤ کے لئے بھی مفید ہیں۔ امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے روایت ہے : دونوں ہاتھ سر پر رکھ کر بہ آواز بلند (سورۂ آل عمران،آیت ۸۳) پڑھے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": 