than Allah’s religion that they seek (to follow), and to Him submits whoever is in the heavens and the earth, willingly or unwillingly, and to Him shall they be returned.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Kya yeh log deen'e Khuda ke alaawa kuchh aur talaash kar rahe hai jab-keh zameen o aasmaan ki saari makhluqaat ba-raza o raghbat (raazi o khushi) ya ba-jabr o karaahat (jabar-dasti) Usi ki bargah mein sar'e tasleem kham kiye (sar jukaaye) huwe hai aur sab ko Usi ki bargah mein waapas jaana hai.", "Urdu": "کیا یہ لوگ دینِ خدا کے علاوہ کچھ اور تلاش کررہے ہیں جب کہ زمین و آسمان کی ساری مخلوقات بہ رضا و رغبت یا بہ جبر وکراہت اسی کی بارگاہ میں سر تسلیم خم کئے ہوئے ہے اور سب کو اسی کی بارگاہ میں واپس جانا ہے۔", "RArabic": "AFAGHAIRA DEENIL LAAHI YABGHOONA WA LAHOOO ASLAMA MAN FIS SAMAAWAATI WAL ARDI TAW’ANW WA KARHANW WA ILAIHI YURJA’OON.", "ArabicText1": "اَفَغَيْرَ دِيْنِ اللهِ يَبْغُوْنَ وَلَهٗٓ اَسْلَمَ مَنْ فِي السَّمٰوٰتِ وَالْاَرْضِ طَوْعًا وَّكَرْهًا وَّاِلَيْهِ يُرْجَعُوْنَ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null